the expansion of the universe is biblically supported.  11 times it says God 'stretched' out the heavens...- it is said 11 times for obvious emphasis.you can scoff all you want at that reference... but what remains is the fact that we have only recently discovered the universes expansion..  the Bible pointed to it all along.  